milestones.description: Steve Tikolo and Odumbe's 118-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 102 between Otieno and Odumbe
Steve Tikolo has scored 5 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for KENYA breaking Hitesh Modi's record
Aminul Islam has become the top scorer for BAN in ODIs with 535 runs, going past Athar Ali Khan's 532
Shahriar Hossain's 95 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BAN), surpassing Athar Ali Khan's 82
Aasif Karim has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (22) for KENYA, going past Hitesh Modi
